      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;my-cv&#34;&gt;My CV&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a repo for my CV, which uses a data-driven approach. In other words, entries are stored as data, which are then read into R and can be rendered in various ways. The entire CV is built with a combination of 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/rstudio/pagedown&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;pagedown&lt;/a&gt;
 with custom HTML and CSS. Basically, this allows PDFs to be generated using HTML and CSS code, as opposedd something like LaTeX.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please feel free to fork/modify as much as you&amp;rsquo;d like, and get in touch if you have any questions.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
